data.description: Welcome to this stunning, modern 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home nestled on a spacious .33-acre lot in a sought-after neighborhood. Boasting contemporary design and ample living space, this residence is a true gem.  Upon entry, you're greeted by a welcoming foyer that leads into an expansive open-concept living area, adorned with sleek hardwood flooring and abundant natural light pouring in through large windows. The living room provides a comfortable space for relaxation and entertainment, seamlessly flowing into the dining area, perfect for hosting gatherings and family meals.The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, a spacious island with breakfast bar seating, and ample cabinet storage, catering to both functionality and style.a generously sized primary bedroom suite, offering a tranquil retreat with a luxurious ensuite bathroom equipped with dual vanities, a soaking tub, and a separate walk-in shower.
